{"word":"G1754 - ἐνεργέω - energéō - en-erg-eh'-o - Do","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνεργέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">energéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-erg-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Do</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விளங்கச்செய், கையாளி, உண்டாக்கு, பலன் செய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to be operative, be at work, put forth power"},{"paragraph":"2. to effect"},{"paragraph":"3. to display one's activity, to show oneself operative"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1756 - ἐνεργής - energḗs - en-er-gace'/1756\">G1756</a>; to <i>be active</i>, <i>efficient:</i> - do, (be) effectual (fervent), be mighty in, shew forth self, work (effectually in).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1753/1753\">G1753</a>, <a href=\"#/G1754/1754\">G1754</a>, <a href=\"#/G1755/1755\">G1755</a>, <a href=\"#/G1756/1756\">G1756</a>, <a href=\"#/G2038/2038\">G2038</a>, <a href=\"#/G2039/2039\">G2039</a>, <a href=\"#/G2040/2040\">G2040</a>, <a href=\"#/G2041/2041\">G2041</a>, <a href=\"#/G2108/2108\">G2108</a>, <a href=\"#/G2109/2109\">G2109</a>, <a href=\"#/G2110/2110\">G2110</a>"}]}